{"id":25651,"date":[{"year":1938,"month":8,"day":8}],"page":"11","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"灯塔","column":"","genre":"","count":"255","ytitle":"","mtitle":"山歌(打矮东洋)","ftitle":"","authors":["疏影"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"疏影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下面一首山歌，在我乡浦东附近，流行甚广，其歌云:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砰!砰!砰!砰!敲门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啥人?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张家小弟弟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"做啥?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"借扁担。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"借仔扁担做啥?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挑落砖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挑仔洛砖做啥?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"磨刀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"磨刀做啥?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劈毛竹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劈仔毛竹做啥?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"押淘罗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"押仔淘罗做啥?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"淘糯米。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"淘仔糯米做啥?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"做圆子。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"做仔圆子啥人吃?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我家大哥吃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃仔做啥?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃仔去打矮东洋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一首山歌，其词是一问一答的，唱的时候，一人或两人均可。如两人唱时，则可以一个做问，一个作答。我从前住在故乡的时候，在这月白风清的晚上，时常有这类的歌声，随风送入我的耳鼓中。我现还记得，所以把它写了出来。"}]}